text:
Hi @FedExHelp - is it possible to see where a truck is in order to judge when an item might be delivered? Tracking info has shown "On FedEx vehicle for delivery
Scheduled for delivery next business day" since Saturday.

@dezeerae Hi, this is Carole. I would be happy to check on your shipment. Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r
